oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Aerial of Crieve Hall and Nolensville Road area, south of Nashville, Tennessee, 1961 January 03
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: An aerial view of the Crieve Hall and Nolensville Road area, south of downtown Nashville, Tennessee. This is a January 3, 1961 aerial view of the neighborhoods and landscapes. Forms part of Record Group 412, Photographs Collection. 1 photograph negative : b & w ; 4 x 5 in.
